Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.00,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'm just awful.}Không được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.69,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh... But you at least managed \Nto play it to the en—}Nhưng cậu đã có thể chơi đến cuối--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.07,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{About that, though!}Về chuyện đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:24.75,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?}V-Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:28.63,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I just realized, I'm supposed \Nto do vocals too, right?}Tớ vừa nhận ra mình còn phải hát nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:32.78,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But I can't sing while I'm focusing \Nall my motor control on the guitar.}Nhưng sao có thể hát khi đang tập trung chơi ghita?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.01,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I... I see...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:38.51,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I was thinking it might be better \Nfor the band if I just sang...}Tớ đã nghĩ mình chỉ nên hát...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.81,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But then I wouldn't have anything \Nto do during interludes,}Nhưng đến thời gian nghỉ giữa hiệp thì phải làm gì,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.58,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{and I'd probably start fidgeting on stage...}tớ sẽ như người thừa trên sân khấu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:44.10,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Oh, um... Yeah!}À ừm... yê!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:45.54,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{So...}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.52,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I guess I'd better work harder!}Tớ đoán mình phải cố hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.32,DefaultItalics,Kita,0,0,0,,{Kit-aura!}Hào quang Kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.26,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{My eyes!}Mắt mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:53.40,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-Nothing.}K-Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.76,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Her eager self-improvement power \Nis too bright to look directly at!}Hào quang sáng chói mình không dám nhìn vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.53,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But are you sure it's all right\Nfor me to sing?}Nhưng nhường tớ hát được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.24,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I know! You should sing with me!}Hay cậu hát chung đi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.25,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-N-Not happening!}K-Không bao giờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.71,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{B-But...}N-Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:10.50,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:10.50,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry. Is it that unpleasant a thought?}Xin lỗi, cậu không thích đến thế nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.98,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Hey, nice one.}Cái đó được đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:14.58,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Is that some new guitar showmanship move?}Đang học màn trình diễn ghita mới hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:15.68,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:16.98,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Do you like it?}Chị thích cái này ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:18.56,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Then I'll practice it too!}Vậy em cũng làm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.64,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You don't need to practice that.}Không cần đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:23.14,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Ryo's here, so let's meet up at the club!}Ryo đến rồi nên tập trung ở Club nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.18,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:28.05,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We will now begin the band meeting!}Chúng ta sẽ bắt đầu họp nhóm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:28.65,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Round of applause!}Vô tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.78,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Now, here's today's topic!}Chủ đề hôm nay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.89,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{The question:}Câu hỏi:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:38.95,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an4\fnArial Black\blur0.3\fs36\c&H080A05&\pos(354.702,75.309)}{How can we be\N more band-like?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.95,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{How can we be more band-like?}Làm gì để giống một ban nhạc?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.45,DefaultItalics,Hitori & Kita,0,0,0,,{It's so half-assed!}Nghe dở hơi vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.48,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked dark, cramped spaces,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.85,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{so I'd bury my face deep in my hood}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.23,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{My eyes resented the heartless world,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.98,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{but yearned for love}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.62,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I liked being soaked by the rain,}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.99,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{because my face looked better clouded over}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.63,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I pretended to be afraid of the storm}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.46,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{while waiting for the sky to burst}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:30.42,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum through the light's distortion}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.84,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to make thunder roar}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:40.64,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum beyond the pain}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.77,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:50.83,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Strum in a harmonizing quartet}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:54.82,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{I want to cause a revolution}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:03:00.83,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{Drum in a lamenting forte}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:05.58,Songs_OP,OP,0,0,0,,{What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.88,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,1)\c&HB3750D&\fnImpact\fs30\pos(238.5,132.5)}{BOCCHI THE ROCK!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.88,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(485,1)\c&HB5780F&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(416.5,255)}#04 Jumping Girl(s)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.96,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an4\fnArial Black\blur0.3\fs30\c&H080A05&\pos(353.564,70.759)}{How can we be\N more band-like?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.73,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Now that we've got a full member lineup,}Giờ thì đông đủ thành viên rồi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.97,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I figured the first order of business \Nwas to get us acting more band-like!}thế nên chúng ta phải gì cho giống một ban nhạc,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.37,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I... I see!}V-Vậy ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:25.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I know practice is crucial,}Chị biết luyện tập cũng quan trọng,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.10,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{but there's gotta be more to us than that!}nhưng thứ này còn hơn nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.98,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I think we should talk \Nabout all kinds of stuff!}Chúng ta nên trò chuyện với nhau nhiều hơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.90,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Is she trying to give Kita-san \Na break from all her practice?}Chị ấy muốn để Kita xả hơi sau khi luyện tập?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.77,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{One tactic is to nail the \Nsuperficial stuff first!}Đầu tiên chúng ta phải hình thành suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:39.01,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Oh, that totally works!}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.32,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Like if you start imitating a new popular \Nmake-up technique and end up looking great!}Giống như khi bắt chước một mẹo\N trang điểm nào đó và nó trở nên tuyệt vời vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.09,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Exactly!}Chính xác!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's like they're speaking \Na foreign language...}Không thể hiểu họ đang nói gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.83,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And with that in mind...}Thế nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.25,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I made us band merch!}Chị đã làm vòng tay ban nhạc!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That's a more superficial \Nstarting point than I expected!}Hiện thực hoá suy nghĩ luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:54.30,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Did you just put a zip tie around your wrist?}Đó chỉ là chị buộc dây quanh cổ tay thôi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.84,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Cute, huh? They come in all colors!}Dễ thương chứ? Nhiều màu lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.64,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{We'll sell them for 500 yen a piece.}Chúng ta sẽ bán với giá 500 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What a ripoff!}Mất đi ý nghĩa ban nhạc vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.76,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{650 if they're signed.}Có chữ kí thì 650.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.10,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{What a steal! I'll take one!}Rẻ quá! Em mua!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Won't that just be circulating \Nmoney within the band?}Vậy khác gì tiền của nhóm về quỹ nhóm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.81,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Anyone else with ideas \Nfor becoming more band-like?}Có ai nghĩ ra ý tưởng gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.25,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I can set us up an Isstagram and run it!}Em có thể tạo insta và đăng bài.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.26,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Great idea!}Ý hay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.31,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I hereby appoint you \NMinister of Social Media!}Chị chỉ định em làm trưởng ban\N quản lý truyền thông xã hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.21,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{And I'll post every day when the time comes!}Và em sẽ đăng bài mỗi ngày!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.49,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.75,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{What about forming a fan club?}Thành lập nhóm hâm mộ thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:25.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That's awfully hasty!}Sao nhanh quá vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.26,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{10,000 yen annual membership fee.}Phí thành viên 10.000 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That's awfully expensive!}Quá mắc!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.54,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Membership perks include meet-and-greets}Đặc quyền bao gồm gặp gỡ và nói chuyện,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:34.11,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{and a once-a-year takoyaki party with the band.}mỗi năm tổ chức tiệc tako 1 lần.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.61,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{The fans bring the ingredients.}Fan mang nguyên liệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.16,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{What a steal! I'll join!}Hay quá! Em tham gia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Kita-chan, you're already in the band.}Kita-chan, em là thành viên ban nhạc rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.19,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{What about you, Gotoh-san?}Còn cậu, Gotou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.78,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Any ideas?}Có ý tưởng nào không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What do I do? I wasn't even thinking!}Sao giờ? Mình chả nghĩ gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:45.84,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Her eyes are so sparkly!}M-Mắt cậu ấy đang lấp lánh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.81,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I feel the burden of expectation!}Ánh mắt kì vọng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.60,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Um... Um...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:55.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-If I don't say something, I... I...}N-Nếu không chế ra gì đó...
