Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A-Am I allowed to just walk in?}M-Mình được phép vào không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.43,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{How do people just walk into places?}Mọi người làm sao có thể vào được chỗ này vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{How do they do it on TV and stuff?}Lại còn quay phim lên TV nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, I know!}A,phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.94,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Are ya winning, diners?}Hey, còn chỗ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.72,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Oh, Bocchi.}A, Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.95,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Over here.}Bên này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-This is awkward.}K-Khó xử quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:08.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, I've never \Nbeen alone with Ryo-san before.}Nghĩ lại thì đây là lần đầu có hai đứa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I don't even know much about her.}Mình chẳng biết gì về chị ấy nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{F-For that matter, why hasn't \Nshe talked to me yet?}C-Cơ mà sao chẳng nói gì nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.01,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{That was delicious.}Ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:16.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She finished eating!}Ăn xong rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What do I do? Should I initiate?}Sao giờ? Mình nói trước nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Nhưng...{But...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.59,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That photo shoot sure was fun, huh?!}Buổi chụp ảnh lúc nãy vui nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.44,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Not really.}Cũng tạm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That could be the result!}Có thể sẽ thành như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.88,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Just show me the lyrics.}Cho chị xem lời đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:41.87,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, right.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.35,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.16,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{No problem. Let's see.}Không có gì. Đưa đây chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.86,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Oh, ohh!}Ừm ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{She's unusually flustered!}Phản ứng bối rối bất thường...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.30,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{This is good.}Được đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure I agree, \Nbut for the band's sake...}Mình không hiểu gì cả nhưng vì ban nhạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.39,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Yes, it's a masterpiece.}Vâng, đó là một kiệt tác.
