Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.63,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Though personally I think one\Nis a bit childish for a band.}Chị nghĩ chữ kí này có hoi trẻ con.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.39,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{That's not the right page!}Không phải trang đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:12.23,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Are you personally satisfied \Nwith these lyrics, Bocchi?}Em cảm thấy thoả mãn với lời nhạc này?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.16,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, w-well...}À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:17.32,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I figured we should do something \Nreally "hit band"-like...}Em nghĩ chúng ta nên làm gì đó kiểu một ban nhạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.12,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\blur1\pos(20,20)\p1\c&HF5F8F5&\fscx300\fscy215\alpha&H33&}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.12,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs12\an7\c&H787C77&\pos(30,30)}{Can't do it anymore\NYou say as you give up on moving forward\NOn a road that seems to go on forever\NIt feels like you'll never arrive anywhere\NAnd that's got you worried, doesn't it?\N\NBut hey now, listen up\NDon't forget you're not alone, that we're all here\NWe're sending you this cheer just as your heart's about to break\N\NYour dreams will come true\NDon't give up until the very end!\NYour dreams will come true\N}{\s1}{Believe in yourself the way you are}{\s0}{\NBelieve in yourself and get walking again!\N\NGlory awaits you ahead, I know it\NFor everyone around the world trying hard, Go for it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.82,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Did I ever tell you?}Chị đã nói chưa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:26.12,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I was in another band a long time ago.}Chị từng ở trong một ban nhạc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:32.08,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Their lyrics were awkward, \Nbut I liked how honest they were.}Lời nhạc của họ rất kinh khủng\N nhưng lại rất thẳng thắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:37.47,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{But, desperate for sales, they started \Ngoing in a more commercial direction.}Tuy nhiên để chiều lòng khách và \Ntăng lượng bán đĩa, họ đã đi sai hướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.34,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I hated that. That's why I quit.}Chị không thích điều đó nên đã rời nhóm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.55,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{We had a little fight about it at the time.}Bọn chị có cãi nhau một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.64,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,Và trong lúc chị đang chán nản...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:53.66,Flashback,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.15,Flashback,Nijika,0,0,0,,{If you've got time, \Nwill you play bass for me?}Nếu rảnh thì tham gia chơi bass cho tớ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.28,Flashback,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.45,Flashback,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Because I love the way you play!}Vì tớ thích cách cậu chơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:06.29,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{When Nijika said that to me, I decided \Nto give playing in a band another try.}Khi Nijika nói thế, chị đã thử làm lại lần nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.42,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Abandoning your uniqueness \Nis equivalent to dying.}Từ bỏ cá tính của bản thân không khác nào đã chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.33,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Ryo-san?}Chị Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:17.42,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{So don't write generic lyrics \Nbased on other concerns.}Thế nên đừng viết mấy lời nhạc chung chung,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.26,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Write what }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ want to write.}hãy viết những gì em muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:25.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-But if I do that, I'll write bitter, \Nsocial-outcast lyrics—}N-Nhưng nếu thế, sẽ thành mấy bài hát cay đắng, u sầu--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:29.30,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{But won't it be hilarious\Nif a normie sings that?}Nhưng với người bình thường có khi lại thấy thú vị?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.69,DefaultItalics,Kita,0,0,0,,{I spend my days cursing you losers!}Mỗi ngày tôi sẽ nguyền rủa lũ thua cuộc!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:37.40,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Bringing a wide variety of individuals \Ntogether into one sound...}Đưa nhiều cá tính khác nhau vào âm nhạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.28,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{That's the color that Kessoku Band will have.}Đó là màu sắc mà Kessoku sẽ hướng đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Ryo-san is actually a considerate person.}Chị ấy là người rất nghiêm túc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.11,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Let's get out of here.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:47.99,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.50,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, Ryo-san...}Chị Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.08,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The check...}Tính tiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.68,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I'm broke. Treat me?}Xin lỗi, chị nghèo rồi. Em trả đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.44,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?}H-Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.27,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-But you're the one who invited me...}N-Nhưng chị là người mời em...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.68,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I just couldn't take another \Nday of eating weeds.}Gần đây chị ăn cỏ nhiều quá hết chịu nổi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.24,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{You're still doing that?!}Vẫn còn ăn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:09.52,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{And this shop just opened, \Nand I wanted to eat here so bad...}Và chỗ này vừa khai trương nên muốn đến ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.31,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Please, treat me?}Làm ơn bao chị đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I t-take back what I said!}M-Mình rút lại câu khi nãy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.80,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I really am sorry. \NI'll pay you back next month.}Xin lỗi em! Tháng sau chị sẽ trả!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.94,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{N-No need to rush...}K-Không cần gấp đâu ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.56,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{U-Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.61,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-I'm going to try my best!}E-Em sẽ cố hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.66,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Sure. Can't wait to see it.}Ừm, chị mong chờ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:44.22,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{U-Um...}À nè...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I f-finished the lyrics...}E-Em đã viết xong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.68,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{H-Here.}Đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.75,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Gotoh-san, are you all right? You look tired.}Gotou, mắt cậu thâm quá. Ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.69,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm fine.}À không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:58.31,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've just been so focused on the lyrics,}Em đã tập trung vào viết lời,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:20:59.94,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I c-completely forgot to sleep...}nên quên ngủ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.66,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Wow!}Ồ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:02.55,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Let's have a look!}Xem thử nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.41,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I can't wait to see the \Nfruits of your labors!}Chị nóng lòng được xem kết quả của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:10.03,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It m-might be... too much of a downer.}C-Có thể nó sẽ tăm tối lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.01,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It certainly is a downer.}Đúng thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:12.95,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,Ryo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:15.85,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{But it's very Bocchi.}Nhưng phong cách Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.26,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It might not connect with too many people,}Tuy không kết nối được nhiều người,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:21.34,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{but those it does, it'll hit deeply.}nhưng chắc chắn sẽ có người nghe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.93,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Where'd this friendship come from?!}Từ khi nào thân thiết vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:33.39,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But these lyrics really are \Nsuper great, Bocchi-chan!}Nhưng lời này tuyệt thật đó, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.25,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I love this phrase here!}Tớ thích chỗ này nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.20,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Same.}Chị cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:47.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I m-managed to figure out the lyrics.}M-Mình đã viết xong lời.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:52.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm going to do my best...}Phải cố gắng lên...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:58.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I hope the band can \Nstay together forever...}Hi vọng ban nhạc sẽ mãi bên nhau...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:03.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{and I can get lots of \Npictures with everyone.}và có thêm nhiều ảnh chụp cùng mọi người...
